sequenceDiagram
    participant Producer as Producer
    participant Leader as Kafka Leader Broker
    participant R1 as Replica 1
    participant R2 as Replica 2
    participant Consumer as Consumer (Group)
    participant Offsets as __consumer_offsets

    Note over Producer,R2: Produce with acks=all
    Producer->>Leader: send(topic, key, value)
    Leader->>Leader: Append to partition log (sequential disk write)
    par Replicate to ISR
        Leader->>R1: Fetch / replicate record
        R1-->>Leader: Ack (in-sync)
    and
        Leader->>R2: Fetch / replicate record
        R2-->>Leader: Ack (in-sync)
    end
    Leader-->>Producer: Ack (offset N)

    Note over Consumer,Leader: Pull-based consume
    loop Poll loop
        Consumer->>Leader: fetch(topic, partition, offset)
        Leader-->>Consumer: Batch [records] via sendfile() zero-copy
        Consumer->>Consumer: Process batch
        Consumer->>Offsets: commit(offset)
    end

    Note over Leader,R1: Leader failure
    alt Leader crashes
        R1->>R1: Promoted to leader (KRaft election)
        Producer->>R1: Retry send (idempotent PID + seq dedupes)
    end
